('2279', 'Boogie Board Rip™', 'Boogie Board Rip™', '<p>\r\n	The Boogie Board Rip&trade; LCD Writing Tablet combines an exceptional, paper-like writing experience with the ability to record your written and drawn images and save them as files. Then connect to a computer and transfer files for editing, organizing, archiving and/or sharing!</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Provides a completely electronic medium for creating and preserving notes/drawings</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Eliminates the burden of unmanageable paper notebooks, notepads, memo pads, and sketch pads</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Reduces paper consumption</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Simplifies organization or notes &ndash; easily search and find saved files by date/name on your PC</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n	Makes writing, drawing and learning fun!</p>\r\n', '<p>\r\n	The Boogie Board Rip&trade; LCD Writing Tablet combines an exceptional, paper-like writing experience with the ability to record your written and drawn images and save them as files. Then connect to a computer and transfer files for editing, organizing, archiving and/or sharing!</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Provides a completely electronic medium for creating and preserving notes/drawings</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Eliminates the burden of unmanageable paper notebooks, notepads, memo pads, and sketch pads</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Reduces paper consumption</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Simplifies organization or notes &ndash; easily search and find saved files by date/name on your PC</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n	Makes writing, drawing and learning fun!</p>\r\n', '', 1.0, 1.0, 4.0, 0, 'write/record/transfer', 'write/record/transfer', 'Boogie Board RIP', '', 'bbrip', 0, 1, 102, 0),
('978-616-7191-32-4', 'RESORTS BY THAI ARCHITECTS : EXOTIC ORIENTAL', 'RESORTS BY THAI ARCHITECTS : EXOTIC ORIENTAL', '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 12px;">รีสอร์ตทั้ง 7 โครงการในหนังสือเล่มนี้ รังสรรค์ขึ้นมาจากประสบการณ์และจิตวิญญาณของสถาปนิกไทย ที่สวยงามและน่าประทับใจ ถ่ายทอดความเป็นตะวันออกได้อย่างชาญฉลาด มีความยิ่งใหญ่อลังการ ผลงานแสดงออกถึงความปราณีตและความพิถีพิถัน สร้างความโดดเด่นให้แก่สถานที่ตั้งทั้งในและต่างประเทศ</span></p>\r\n', '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size: 12px;">This book brings together seven resorts from Thailand, Bhutan, Lao and Malaysia that have their origin in the creative thinking and expertise of well-known Thai architects. These exquisite places stand out for their marvelous architecture and interior designs. Both unique and remarkable, these projects deserve to be publicized and appreciated as proudly representative of Thailand. This title focuses on wonderful resorts from Southeast Asia, and includes the following:</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	The Mandarin Oriental Dhara Dhevi Chiang Mai, Thailand/ Hotel de la Paix Luang Prabang, Laos/ Renaissance Phuket Resort &amp; Spa, Thailand/ Six Senses Destination Spa Phuket, Thailand/ Paresa Resort Phuket, Thailand/ Taj Tashi Hotel, Bhutan/ Four Seasons Resort Langkawi, Malaysia</p>\r\n', '', 22.0, 30.0, 3.0, 0, '', '', 'RESORTS BY THAI ARCHITECTS : EXOTIC ORIENTAL', '', 'resorts-by-thai-architects-exotic-oriental', 1, 1, 120, 0),
