ent&quot; (ชำระค่าบริการ)</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-top: 0.02in; margin-bottom: 0.02in;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:11px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><font class="Apple-style-span">4. Enter GOODJOB Comp code &quot;40319&quot;</font></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-top: 0.02in; margin-bottom: 0.02in;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:11px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><font class="Apple-style-span">5. Input your refernce number indicated in the order confirmation as 16 digits number.</font></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-top: 0.02in; margin-bottom: 0.02in;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:11px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><font class="Apple-style-span">6. Key in amount.</font></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-top: 0.02in; margin-bottom: 0.02in;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:11px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><font class="Apple-style-span">7. Re-check your payment details and confirm.</font></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-top: 0.02in; margin-bottom: 0.02in;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:11px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><font class="Apple-style-span">8. Done. You shall recieve slip, please keep it until you recieve your shipment.</font></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-top: 0.02in; margin-bottom: 0.02in;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:11px;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-top: 0.02in; margin-bottom: 0.02in;">\r\n	<strong>ATM BARCODE</strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-top: 0.02in; margin-bottom: 0.02in;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:11px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">Easily follow these steps.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 0.5in; margin-top: 0.02in; margin